As the spirit of {{ill|Saturn|ja|土星|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saturn|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saturn|qq=}} (鎮星), Taion Shin embodies the element of {{ill|Earth (Wu Xing)|ja|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth (Wu Xing)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth (Wu Xing)|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth (wuxing)|qq=}} (陰). Her nature contrasts with the masculine quality of "陽," and she harbors jealousy toward activities related to feminine matters. Consequently, actions concerning women, such as marriages and childbirth, in the direction of her presence are considered inauspicious. However, endeavors related to {{ill|learning|ja|学問|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/learning|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/learning|qq=}} and {{ill|arts|ja|芸術|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/arts|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/arts|qq=}} are deemed auspicious.
